{"tid":1634222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣撚入，有方法增加接觸率","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:43:45.000Z","uid":89667,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bc653933727426e4ea94c214055febad2acfd3eb","tid":1634222,"uid":89667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:58:22.000Z","msg":"話說我頭先去廁所見到呢樣嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SbkH9J2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSbkH9J2.jpg&h=4d82714c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家可以試下喺廁所門後痴文宣<br />\n1. 增加接觸率<br />\n咩人而家仲會行商場？港豬同遊客。佢地平時行過連儂牆未必會停低睇，但去廁所時成份文宣喺佢面前點都會睇到。<br />\nsuggest文宣：解釋點解要搞美心/ 黨鐵 &gt; 日程表 &gt; 呼籲罷買 等等<br />\n最好係英文/ 中英對照，比遊客睇到<br />\n2. 減低手足被藍絲打嘅機會<br />\n去廁所時痴文宣唔會比人打/ 影，因為個廁格入面得你一個，下一手亦無法證明係你痴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"d98e67e6fd57c3b7f9022cb4c4c02539c4243bd7","tid":1634222,"uid":180719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:58:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c448c43cc9ac5ba65d407731dba8fff6e297e034","tid":1634222,"uid":89667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:59:20.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6f15101762a4950d020d34885bf6cd2c225c1671","tid":1634222,"uid":180719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:59:23.000Z","msg":"幫推十連 1/10"},{"pid":"b5964c9dd193b445cc827c5318d3352ae299bb3f","tid":1634222,"uid":89667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:59:32.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"0128baddfa6ca14645fae7124b4b827c85e3c4a8","tid":1634222,"uid":180719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:59:35.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"89f658baf5d1dc93031b500ff91a55cb58f8dd59","tid":1634222,"uid":20076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:59:39.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"9c39f39c85273a9ee0904b5a9b9f2f7da9ddd4ef","tid":1634222,"uid":89667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,